<font face=arial>
---------------------------------------------
Surf_spacedout2 by Buck Nasty
Skybox by AngryBeaver
---------------------------------------------

Yes, Spaced Out 2!
Completely rebuilt from the bottom to top (from scratch) this map has all new structures, smooth ramps, and a new jail.

The Updates...
- Guns with ammo.
- Guns: m3, mp5, ump45, ak47, m4a1, aug, krieg,  awp, and nades (but they aren't guns).
- New jail kill, uses dustmotes rather than laggy smoke.
- Whole new jail.
- New spawn platforms and structures.
- Secret awp room (its not that much of a secret though).
- Bombsite to end epicly long rounds.

- Thanks to Paper-cut for some help with the ramps.

This map will be on the cycle at my server @ css.nyfiber.net:30000
Join my Steam Group @ http://steamcommunity.com/groups/bucknastysurf

-- Buck Nasty
